    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他会带回不太严格的汽车排放标准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-he-ll-return-less-stringent-auto-emissions-standards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他希望恢复较弱的汽车排放标准，将前总统乔·拜登（Joe Biden）施加的车辆污染路线对汽车制造商来说太繁重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-he-ll-return-less-stringent-auto-emissions-standards</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:08:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国迫使1000家公司在黑客之后进行网络辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/uk-to-compel-1-000-firms-to-shore-up-cyber-defenses-after-hacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府将通过立法迫使公司为关键的国家基础设施提供IT服务，以改善其网络防御，并在俄罗斯，中国，伊朗和朝鲜发动攻击之后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/uk-to-compel-1-000-firms-to-shore-up-cyber-defenses-after-hacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国食品通货膨胀率九个月高，增加了对劳动的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/uk-food-inflation-at-nine-month-high-adds-to-pressure-on-labour</link>
      <description><![CDATA[商店橱柜主食和酒精饮料的价格上涨使英国的食品通货膨胀提高了9个月，因为该国的工党政府面临着对生活成本的政治压力的日益增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/uk-food-inflation-at-nine-month-high-adds-to-pressure-on-labour</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Le Pen选举禁令威胁法国政治中脆弱的和平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/le-pen-election-ban-threatens-fragile-peace-in-french-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[海洋勒庞（Marine Le Pen）的选举禁令有法国反建立情绪的激增，这可能会破坏稳定美国吱吱作响的公共财政的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/le-pen-election-ban-threatens-fragile-peace-in-french-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划在第一次外国旅行中访问沙特阿拉伯，阿联酋，卡塔尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-plans-visit-to-saudi-arabia-uae-qatar-on-foreign-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，第二任期的第一次总统旅行可能包括访问沙特阿拉伯，阿拉伯联合酋长国和卡塔尔，以及其他停留。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-plans-visit-to-saudi-arabia-uae-qatar-on-foreign-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:43:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普弗里德曼（Floats Floats Floats Floats）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-floats-friedman-grenell-as-possible-picks-for-un-envoy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统浮动了前美国驻以色列戴维·弗里德曼（David Friedman）和特使里克·格雷内尔（Ric Grenell）作为联合国大使的潜在选秀权，此前一个狭窄的众议院共和党多数派撤销了代表埃利斯·斯特凡尼克（Elise Stefanik）的提名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-floats-friedman-grenell-as-possible-picks-for-un-envoy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:41:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚反对派希望银行监管机构释放贷款规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/australia-opposition-wants-bank-regulator-to-ease-loan-standards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的中央反对派将敦促美国的银行监管机构缓解其抵押贷款标准，以便允许更多的人在下个月赢得办公室的情况下借用房屋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/australia-opposition-wants-bank-regulator-to-ease-loan-standards</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:33:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普针对门票剥皮，新行政命令的费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-to-target-ticket-scalping-fees-with-new-executive-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周一签署了一项行政命令，旨在打破票务剥头和费用，以增加参加消费者现场活动的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-to-target-ticket-scalping-fees-with-new-executive-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 20:42:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈佛受到特朗普威胁，有90亿美元的危险资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-administration-to-review-billions-in-grants-to-harvard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的政府扩大了反对精英大学的竞选活动，威胁要仔细研究为哈佛大学的数十亿美元的联邦资金，这是在冻结哥伦比亚大学的几周后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-administration-to-review-billions-in-grants-to-harvard</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 19:48:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国制裁更多的香港官员在中国的镇压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-sanctions-more-hong-kong-officials-amid-beijing-led-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府正在批准六名中国和香港官员，包括该市司法部长和警察专员，以针对实施北京强硬政策的当局的最新步骤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-sanctions-more-hong-kong-officials-amid-beijing-led-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 17:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
